---
import Section from "../ui/Section.astro";
---

<Section id="faq" title="FAQs">
  <div class="grid grid--2">
    <div class="card">
      <details open>
        <summary>When will I see results?</summary>
        <p class="muted">You may start to notice subtle changes within a few weeks, especially in muscle awareness and facial tension. Visible improvements typically develop with consistent practice over time. Results vary depending on individual habits and consistency.</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Is it safe?</summary>
        <p class="muted">Yes, the program is designed to be gentle and non-invasive. It focuses on natural facial movement, awareness, and balance. However, it is not a medical treatment and should not replace professional medical advice.</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Do I need any equipment?</summary>
        <p class="muted">No, you don’t need any special equipment. All techniques are designed to be done using your hands and your own facial muscles.</p>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <details open>
        <summary>How much time do I need per day?</summary>
        <p class="muted">The routine takes approximately 10–15 minutes per day. Consistency is more important than intensity.</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>How do I access the course?</summary>
        <p class="muted">After purchase, you will receive an email with access to all lessons. You can watch them anytime, at your own pace.</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Is this a replacement for injections or treatments?</summary>
        <p class="muted">No, this is a natural, non-invasive approach focused on supporting your facial structure from within. It does not replace medical or cosmetic procedures.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    details{ padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-2); }
    details:last-child{ border-bottom: none; }
    summary{
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: 18px;
      list-style: none;
      outline: none;
    }
    summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
    summary::after{
      content:"+";
      float:right;
      color: rgba(17,17,17,0.55);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    details[open] summary::after{ content:"–"; }
    p{ margin: 10px 0 0; }
  </style>
</Section>
